{"tid":264440,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] Vienna去Hallstatt最抵屌既方法","createTime":"2017-05-30T22:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T13:56:28.000Z","uid":37278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"406420803775ac6d36f9836b982d7b2263077c60","tid":264440,"uid":37278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T22:01:56.000Z","msg":"黎緊3/6下晝-6/6夜晚會係維也納<br />\n之前因為覺得獨遠就唔諗住去Hallstatt而三日住宿係哂維也納 但之後聽個frd講話果到真係好靚好靚 依家係去緊布達佩斯既途中心郁郁<br />\n有無巴打可以分享下Hallstatt點樣<br />\n頭先上OEBB砌到最平既組合係<br />\n4/6 Wien-Hallstatt 05:55-09:24<br />\n       Hallstatt-Wien 19:14-00:30<br />\n咁樣加埋53.3euro 即日來回抵唔抵<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017e6209f7ddbda9417d3c7b94dd6b3b35991e31","tid":264440,"uid":37278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T22:09:25.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到係咪其實清晨同黃昏最靚？<br />\n咁即日來回即係麻麻地?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9367eadb973f0d550c8924d63c916578e7df7c7c","tid":264440,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T22:13:50.000Z","msg":"咁啱我依家係hallstatt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度個景好靚 但其實得一條大街行 行半日就行完 但個景夠你望好耐<br />\n同埋呢度交通唔方便 好早就無車無船 船好似5點幾就無<br />\n如果你即日來回就要買最早同最遲個班船 同埋hallstatt market個碼頭啲船去train station係會夾好train嘅時間"},{"pid":"7b96b97ff1c1d47459984f6d30967c841ef70f41","tid":264440,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T22:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱睇到係咪其實清晨同黃昏最靚？<br />\n咁即日來回即係麻麻地?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃昏好晏 你會無船搭去train station 清晨一樣 4點幾5點 都係睇唔到 清朝黃昏都靚 但呢幾日都落雨 難睇啲啦"},{"pid":"544258c3614fa811428572797255c8178cd3219a","tid":264440,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T22:21:41.000Z","msg":"去游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去完先知個度咁出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ba9837a5e494c0be55b46ca827f39d97ac9a08","tid":264440,"uid":37278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁啱我依家係hallstatt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度個景好靚 但其實得一條大街行 行半日就行完 但個景夠你望好耐<br />\n同埋呢度交通唔方便 好早就無車無船 船好似5點幾就無<br />\n如果你即日來回就要買最早同最遲個班船 同埋hallstatt market個碼頭啲船去train station係會夾好train嘅時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實我上面果個plan 9點幾去到7點幾走應該都係有船既？ 船要坐幾耐先到 好易暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw依幾日落住雨既話其實抵唔抵去"},{"pid":"21eb27aa2f3d953f830238bec6dd1857968db514","tid":264440,"uid":87829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁啱我依家係hallstatt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度個景好靚 但其實得一條大街行 行半日就行完 但個景夠你望好耐<br />\n同埋呢度交通唔方便 好早就無車無船 船好似5點幾就無<br />\n如果你即日來回就要買最早同最遲個班船 同埋hallstatt market個碼頭啲船去train station係會夾好train嘅時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實我上面果個plan 9點幾去到7點幾走應該都係有船既？ 船要坐幾耐先到 好易暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw依幾日落住雨既話其實抵唔抵去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後班船由Hallstatt開係六點幾鐘㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實半日喺Hallstatt係夠你行哂成條村幾次嘅<br />\n留幾耐就睇巴打自己喜歡喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我上個禮拜去天氣唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都覺得真係好靚㗎<br />\n<br />\n同埋個Salt mine都好值得去嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申：上個禮拜去過Vienna同Hallstatt"},{"pid":"4853ff0073b6b68c7a0cb4baa